lead_paragraph: Mercedes drivers Lewis Hamilton and Nico Rosberg will remain free to race each other for the Formula One world championship  despite their costly last lap collision in Austria, the team said on Thursday.

headline.print_headline: Colliding Mercedes Drivers Free to Race On
headline.main: Colliding Mercedes Drivers Free to Race On
